        public void setOutdoorPositioningEnabled(boolean enabled)
        Enable or disable outdoor positioning. If it is enabled you get a LOCATION_UPDATE Message via Gateway, each time a new outdoor position is calculated. The frequency is set by setOutdoorPositioninginterval.
        Parameters:
        enabled: - true if you want to enable this feature, false if you want to disable
